{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-20T11:23:16.531Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Core idea: "},{"type":"hardBreak"},{"type":"text","text":"Instead of seeing Claude as a command‑taking chatbot or a “magic 8‑ball,” treat it like a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"high‑performing teammate"},{"type":"text","text":" who needs clear context, boundaries, and goals to do great work."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Anthropic explicitly says:"}]},{"type":"blockquote","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"“When interacting with Claude, think of it as a brilliant but very new employee (with amnesia) who needs explicit instructions.”"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"That’s the collaborative mindset: you’re not just firing questions; you’re "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"briefing a partner"},{"type":"text","text":" who can reason, critique, and co‑create, but only if you give it enough to work with."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"What this mindset looks like in practice"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"1. From “give me a result” to “let’s build something together”"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Old mindset (chatbot):"}]},{"type":"blockquote","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"“Write me a blog post about AI.”"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Collaborator mindset (teammate):"}]},{"type":"blockquote","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"“You’re my content strategist. We’re building a blog post for city officials about urban planning and AI."}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"First, propose 5 specific angles with a short thesis for each."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Wait for my feedback."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Then we’ll outline and write the full post together.”"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You’re treating Claude as a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"thought partner"},{"type":"text","text":" who can generate ideas, critique, and refine—not just a result machine."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"2. Be explicit, but friendly and cooperative"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Anthropic’s rule:"}]},{"type":"blockquote","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"“Claude does not have context on your norms, styles, guidelines, or preferred ways of working. The more precisely you explain what you want, the better Claude’s response will be.”"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Collaborative framing:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Don’t: “Just write something good.”"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Do: “You’re a senior copywriter. Write a 3‑paragraph email to trial users who didn’t convert."}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tone: friendly but professional."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Audience:务实 tech managers."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Goal: get them to try the analytics feature."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this product description and this example email as a template.”"}]}]}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You’re explicit about "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"who, what, why, and how"},{"type":"text","text":", but the tone is like briefing a colleague, not ordering a servant."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"3. Break work into stages (Outline → Refine → Write)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A key collaborative pattern is: "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"don’t ask for perfection in one shot."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Single-shot (chatbot):"}]},{"type":"blockquote","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"“Write a full proposal for a new feature.”"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Collaborative workflow:"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Plan:"}]},{"type":"blockquote","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"“First, propose an outline with 5 sections and a short thesis for each. Don’t write the full text yet.”"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":2,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Refine:"}]},{"type":"blockquote","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"“Based on my feedback, revise the outline and add bullet points for key ideas in each section.”"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":3,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Write:"}]},{"type":"blockquote","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"“Now write the full proposal, following the approved outline.”"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This is like working with a teammate at a whiteboard: you "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"iterate together"},{"type":"text","text":", catching mistakes early instead of rewriting a huge document later."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"4. Give Claude permission to think, not just respond fast"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Collaborative prompting includes "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"explicit thinking space"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"“Think step by step before giving your final answer.”"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"“Critique your own response against these criteria before showing it to me.”"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Use tags like "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"<thinking>"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"<answer>"},{"type":"text","text":" so Claude can jot down its reasoning first."}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This is like telling a colleague:"}]},{"type":"blockquote","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"“Before you present your solution, sketch your reasoning and double‑check it against the constraints.”"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"It’s not about making Claude slow; it’s about making it "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"more careful and more useful"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"5. Assign roles that unlock expertise"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Anthropic calls this "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"role prompting"},{"type":"text","text":" and says it’s the most powerful way to use system prompts with Claude:"}]},{"type":"blockquote","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"“Assign the chatbot a specific role, like ‘news editor’ or ‘financial planner.’ This technique can significantly boost Claude’s performance in complex scenarios like legal analysis or financial modeling.”"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Collaborator framing:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"“You are a senior security engineer reviewing a contract for cloud services.”"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"“You are a data scientist analyzing this dataset and explaining trends to a non‑technical manager.”"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You’re not just saying “act like”; you’re "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"invoking a whole set of expectations"},{"type":"text","text":" (vocabulary, depth, perspective) just like you’d when assigning a task to a specialist colleague."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"6. Use examples as “shared work patterns,” not tricks"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Few‑shot / multi‑shot prompting is often described as a “trick,” but in the collaborator mindset it’s more like:"}]},{"type":"blockquote","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"“Here’s how we’ve done this before; let’s follow the same pattern.”"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Anthropic says:"}]},{"type":"blockquote","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"“Examples are your secret weapon shortcut for getting Claude to generate exactly what you need. By providing a few well‑crafted examples, you can dramatically improve accuracy, consistency, and quality.”"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example pattern:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Task: Classify emails into Billing, Bug, Feature, or Other.\n\nExamples:\nEmail: \"I was double charged this month.\"\n→ Category: Billing\nReason: The email is about incorrect charging.\n\nEmail: \"The app crashes when I click Export.\"\n→ Category: Bug\nReason: A specific feature is crashing.\n\nNow classify this email:\n\"Can you add a Google Sheets export option?\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You’re showing Claude "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"your team’s style"},{"type":"text","text":", not justStuff it to memorize."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"7. Let Claude challenge you, not just agree"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A true collaborator doesn’t just say “yes”; they "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"push for better outcomes"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"In the collaborator mindset, you deliberately ask:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"“What’s wrong with this approach?”"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"“What edge cases am I missing?”"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"“If you were my skeptical reviewer, what would you critique?”"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This breaks through the default “polite assistant” behavior and unlocks "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"transformative insights"},{"type":"text","text":", not just comfortable answers."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Contrasting mindsets: Chatbot vs Collaborator"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":"left"},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Aspect"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":"left"},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Chatbot mindset"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":"left"},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Collaborator mindset"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Goal"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Get a quick answer"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Build something better together"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Instructions"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Vague: “Write something good”"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Explicit: role, task, audience, format, constraints"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Workflow"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"One-shot: “do it all”"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Multi-stage: outline → refine → write → review"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Thinking"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"“Just answer”"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"“Think step by step; critique your own response”"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Role"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"“Generic assistant”"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"“Senior engineer / editor / analyst”"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Examples"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"None or haphazard"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Curated, few‑shot examples showing your style"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Feedback"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"“Fix it”"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"“Here’s what’s missing; let’s iterate together”"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Why this mindset works so well with Claude"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Claude is already "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"fine‑tuned to be helpful, honest, and cooperative"},{"type":"text","text":", and it responds especially well to:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Clear, direct instructions"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Structured prompts (XML tags, lists, schemas)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Few‑shot examples"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Step‑by‑step reasoning and self‑critique"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"These are all "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"natural in a collaborative relationship"},{"type":"text","text":" where you’re working with someone who:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Has strong reasoning but no context of your world"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Needs explicit boundaries to avoid hallucinations"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Benefits from multi‑turn feedback loops like real colleagues"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Anthropic’s internal code team uses this mindset daily:"}]},{"type":"blockquote","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"“90–95% of Anthropic’s internal code is now AI‑generated. Our bottleneck has shifted from writing code to decision‑making and code review.”"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"That’s a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"team dynamic"},{"type":"text","text":", not a chatbot."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Simple “collaborator” prompt template you can use"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You can turn this into a mental habit for almost any task:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"yaml"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"You are a [role] (e.g. senior TypeScript engineer, marketing strategist, risk analyst).\n\nGoal:\nWe’re working on [specific goal]. This will be used for [audience/context] to achieve [outcome].\n\nConstraints:\n- Tone: [friendly, formal, skeptical, etc.]\n- Length: [X words / X sections]\n- Format: [JSON with fields A, B, C / Markdown with headings / bullet list]\n- Do not: [hallucinate API endpoints / make up facts / use external sources]\n\nProcess:\n1) First, propose an outline / plan with 3–5 items.\n2) Wait for my feedback.\n3) Then refine and write the full output.\n4) Before finalizing, critique your response against these criteria: [list].\n\nHere is the context:\n<context>\n[docs, data, examples, etc.]\n</context>"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This template embodies the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"collaborator mindset"},{"type":"text","text":": role + shared goal + explicit constraints + multi‑stage process + self‑critique."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Once you consistently treat Claude as a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"brilliant new teammate who needs explicit briefings and iterative feedback"},{"type":"text","text":", your prompts naturally become clearer, more structured, and more powerful—and Claude’s responses improve dramatically as a result."}]}]}}
